Package model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Bag
    Interface for the Person typed Bags with add and delete methods.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Admin
    Extension of Person class with the automatically set type as 2.
    AdminBag
    Class used to store an ArrayList of Admins.
    Course
    Contains all the info regarding a course
    CourseBag
    Class that holds an ArrayList of Courses
    Database
    Database class can read from the text files and store data into them such as Persons and Majors.
    Faculty
    Person subclass class that automatically sets type to 1
    FacultyBag
    Bag class that holds an ArrayList for Faculty
    Major
    Class that hold values for a major
    MajorBag
    Bag class that holds an ArrayList of Majors
    Person
    Superclass to Student, Faculty and Admin classes
    PersonBag
    Bag class that holds an ArrayList of Persons
    Student
    A subclass of Person object and automatically sets type to 0
    StudentBag
    Bag class that holds an ArrayList of Students
